value: Breeds on the Black and Caspian Seas, Sea of Azov, Persian Gulf, Makran coast and Sind; southern Spain(?). Ranges throughout the Medi- terranean, coast of northwestern Africa and the Red Sea.
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World

value: Resident and visitor, coasts: breeds scattered Senegal - Egypt; disperses all along Red Sea.
Mediterranean basin to nw India; winters to ne Africa
